The paper focuses on the intersection of computer vision and natural language processing, specifically on the task of generating natural questions about an image. This falls under the scope of several CS sub-categories, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
